up in surgery.

165
00:06:38,832 --> 00:06:40,872
Next show time
is 15 minutes out.
I could use it.

166
00:06:40,901 --> 00:06:43,471
I gotta get this bleeding
under control. What's the
status on your guy?

167
00:06:43,504 --> 00:06:45,714
Take her up.
Take the gunshot.

168
00:06:45,739 --> 00:06:46,839
Hold on.

169
