His airway's so damaged,
I can't even do a tracheotomy.

170
00:06:48,609 --> 00:06:50,509
He's got five minutes
until anoxic brain dead.

171
00:06:50,544 --> 00:06:52,014
Mine's got pressure.
I'll see what I can do here.

172
00:06:52,045 --> 00:06:54,845
You're scrubbing in
with me.

173
00:06:54,882 --> 00:06:57,122
**

174
00:06:57,150 --> 00:07:00,720
