her transverse colon

215
00:08:33,046 --> 00:08:34,176
at the
splenic flexure.

216
00:08:34,214 --> 00:08:35,684
Put it
on our to-do list.

217
00:08:35,716 --> 00:08:36,916
[ Monitor beeping ]

218
00:08:36,950 --> 00:08:39,950
Why does her boyfriend think
it's your fault?

219
00:08:41,088 --> 00:08:43,588
It punctured
her diaphragm here

220
00:08:43,624 --> 00:08:45,564
and entered
the posterior chest.

221
00:08:47,595 --> 00:08:48,925
[ Monitor beeping rapidly ]

222
00:08:48,962 --> 00:08:50,062
She's bleeding again.
Clamp the hilum.

223
00:08:50,097 --> 00:08:51,327
I already did.
It's too damaged to hold.

224
00:08:51,364 --> 00:08:53,334
Gauze!

225
00:08:53,366 --> 00:08:56,336
**

226
00:08:56,369 --> 00:08:57,969
Hold this right there.
Don't let go.

227
00:08:58,005 --> 00:09:00,205
Oh, this isn't
gonna work.

228
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:02,580
It's gonna be like sewing
ground beef back into a steak.

229
00:09:02,610 --> 00:09:04,040
All right, new plan --
she's gonna have to live
without her spleen.

230
00:09:04,077 --> 00:09:05,047
To pick up.

231
00:09:05,078 --> 00:09:07,008
[ Beeping continues ]

232
00:09:07,047 --> 00:09:09,217
Need a ligating suture
on the splenic artery

233
00:09:09,249 --> 00:09:10,679
while I make
the cut.

234
00:09:10,718 --> 00:09:11,748
Can you
do that for me

235
00:09:11,785 --> 00:09:13,685
before this young lady
bleeds out on us, Murphy?

236
00:09:13,721 --> 00:09:14,791
Yes.

237
00:09:14,822 --> 00:09:20,562
**

238
00:09:46,286 --> 00:09:50,656
